        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="0"/>
                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">arci</ex></expan> &amp;lt;f=P&amp;gt;(ilius)<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Lae<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">tus</supplied> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">IIvir</supplied> muru<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">m long(um) p(edes) --- ex? d(ecreto)? d(ecurionum)? f(aciendum)? c(uravit)</supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich überliefert. Z. 1: statt M(arci) &amp;lt;f=P&amp;gt;(ilius)(?) auch M(arcus?) P(orcius)(?) oder M(arcus?) P(ompeius)(?), statt Lae[tus?] auch Lae[tinus?] oder Lae[vinus?] denkbar. Z. 2: statt ex? d(ecreto)? d(ecurionum)? f(aciendum)? c(uravit)? auch d(e)? s(ua)? p(ecunia)? fecit? (oder refecit?) möglich.</p>
            </div>
